I haven't really checked
on advocacy groups in Cameroon,

00:40:02.020 --> 00:40:06.820
but I am sure there are groups
 that you can work with in Cameroon.

00:40:09.860 --> 00:40:11.260
Yigakpoa: Thank you so much, Femi.

00:40:11.460 --> 00:40:13.740
We have another question from Gerson.

00:40:13.900 --> 00:40:18.540
They say, "What's the general feedback
and reception of businesses

00:40:18.700 --> 00:40:23.180
and websites owners in Kenya
regarding digital accessibility?

00:40:23.900 --> 00:40:27.460
Is it well-received and implemented
 or is there resistance?"

00:40:28.860 --> 00:40:31.820
Femi: Yes, it is well-received.

00:40:31.940 --> 00:40:35.740
There is some resistance,
 as there will also be.

00:40:35.820 --> 00:40:44.020
As in the United States and in Europe,
it is a standard and it is a law.

00:40:44.140 --> 00:40:49.700
It is something you have to follow
or you will be penalised in some way.

00:40:50.500 --> 00:40:58.820
Even for those who do not want
to follow, it is very important.

00:40:58.980 --> 00:41:03.620
Also, as I mentioned,

00:41:03.740 --> 00:41:08.260
that one of the reasons
 why this was pushed

00:41:08.380 --> 00:41:11.940
was due to the COVID-19 pandemic

00:41:12.060 --> 00:41:15.820
and a lot of people
 actually could see a genuine

00:41:16.020 --> 00:41:20.900
and a good reason
 for implementing this standard.

00:41:21.020 --> 00:41:26.700
Also, with the fact that--
I think someone else talked about this,

00:41:26.820 --> 00:41:29.380
I've also talked about this in my previous talk,

00:41:29.500 --> 00:41:34.060
is if there are standards
and laws like this

00:41:34.180 --> 00:41:35.700
and you are not following them,

00:41:35.780 --> 00:41:40.780
you are basically not reaching people
with disabilities.

00:41:40.900 --> 00:41:45.140
If you are a business, maybe you sell online

00:41:45.300 --> 00:41:47.100
and you are not implementing the standard,

00:41:47.220 --> 00:41:51.660
it means you are not reaching
 about 15% of your customers.

00:41:51.740 --> 00:41:56.700
So I think these are the things
 that people actually get

00:41:56.780 --> 00:42:00.220
to think about and then we have
 to follow the standard.

